Let's chat briefly about collaboration and why it's so important.

00:00:09.179 --> 00:00:12.685
I mean, it's got to be important if we're creating an entire course on it.

00:00:12.685 --> 00:00:15.990
Well, collaboration is incredibly beneficial because most of

00:00:15.990 --> 00:00:20.254
the time you won't be working by yourself as a lone developer on a project.

00:00:20.254 --> 00:00:21.765
You'll be working with a team,

00:00:21.765 --> 00:00:23.594
maybe with people you don't even know,

00:00:23.594 --> 00:00:26.554
or maybe you're contributing to an open-source project.

00:00:26.553 --> 00:00:30.119
